title: 2019 CFB Week 14 Slate - Rivalry Week
description:
El Pres, Big Cat & Rico Bosco return for another week of picks. There was a lot of tension in the room over a certain t-shirt being sold in the Barstool store, Dave is coming off one of his worst gambling weeks ever where he went down 45 units and Big Cat just wants everyone to get along and get fired up for Rivalry Week!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
